=== Building OLA ===
* Download the pre-reqs:
 apt-get install libncurses5-dev libmicrohttpd-dev libcppunit-dev uuid-dev protobuf-dev
* Download the code:
 wget http://linux-lighting.googlecode.com/files/ola-0.8.6.tar.gz
* Build:
 tar xzf ola-0.8.6.tar.gz
 cd ola-0.8.6
 ./configure
 make
 make install

=== Running OLA ===
Get some info on what you have plugged in:
 ola_dev_info

